These are Puzzles for 3x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-1::.
House: futuristic, cottage, townhouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, march, february
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, aristoff, davidoff
1. the davidoff-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the futuristic house is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
5. the townhouse house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3     |
| House   | townhouse       | futuristic     | cottage    |
| Birthday   | february   | march          | april   |
| Cigar         | dannemann | davidoff | aristoff |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane, train
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, blend, fonseca
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, rock, punk
1. the fan of punk is the person driving the train##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the fan of rock is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
5. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Transport    | quad-bike     | train  | airplane  |
| Cigar   | fonseca | blend | davidoff    |
| Music-Genre     | gospel      | punk    | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, ferret
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, drawing, card-games
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, 7up
1. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |   3    |
| Pet          | hamster         | ferret     | chinchilla   |
| Hobby   | drawing       | traveling     | card-games |
| Beverage         | 7up | fanta | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, blue, yellow
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding, tennis
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, asparagus, broccoli
1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2     |       3       |
| Color   | fuchsia | yellow  | blue |
| Sport        | tennis | snowboarding  | ice-hockey |
| Food        | pomegranate | asparagus | broccoli         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, poppy, orchid
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, november
City: paris, marseilles, new-york
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
4. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
5. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |
| Flower   | orchid | aconite  | poppy  |
| Birthday   | august  | february | november |
| City           | marseilles  | new-york    | paris    |

