.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, security-guard, fisherman
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, romance, mystery
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, brazilian, japanese
1. the freelancer is between the japanese and the person watching mystery movies##2
2. the person watching satire movies is the security-guard##1
3. the freelancer is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the brazilian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |      3      |
| Job    | fisherman  | freelancer  | security-guard        |
| Movie-Genre       | mystery | romance | satire |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | brazilian   | japanese   |

