.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, malaysian, australian
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, red, fuchsia
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, tea, mirinda
1. the malaysian is between the person who likes blood-red and the australian##2
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
4. the malaysian is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |    3    |
| Nationality   | indian | malaysian        | australian |
| Color           | blood-red   | red      | fuchsia     |
| Beverage         | mirinda | tea | almond-milk    |

