.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, romance, horror
City: new-york, nizza, rome
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, goldfish
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the owner of the cat is between the person traveling to rome and the person watching horror movies##2
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
4. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
5. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2     |      3       |
| Movie-Genre    | documentary   | romance | horror       |
| City     | rome  | new-york  | nizza |
| Pet   | rat | cat  | goldfish       |

