.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-9::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, train
House: tower, ranch-style, townhouse
The people have 3 different jobs:  mechanic, scientist, manager
1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the tower house is in an odd position##4
3. the ranch-style house is on the left or right of the scientist##3
4. the tower house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the person driving the tram is between the mechanic and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |       3       |
| Transport         | helicopter | tram | train |
| House   | townhouse       | ranch-style  | tower     |
| Job           | scientist     | manager     | mechanic          |

