.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, ebony, blue
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, horse, turtle
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, roller, snowmobile
1. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the horse is the owner of the horse##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
6. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3    |
| Color           | blue | apricot        | ebony   |
| Pet   | horse | turtle | chinchilla    |
| Transport   | snowmobile         | tram      | roller |

