3. the palace house is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the french is on the left of the russian##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2      |    3    |
| Nationality         | german | french      | russian  |
| House         | craftsman         | palace      | art-deco    |
| Color   | blood-red         | mauve | turquise |

