.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-12::.
3 different games are played: poker, scrabble, go
3 different pets are kept: goat, rat, horse
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, pear, papaya
1. the owner of the rat is the person playing go##1
2. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
3. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |      3       |
| Game         | scrabble        | poker  | go      |
| Pet           | horse | goat | rat |
| Food   | pear        | broccoli   | papaya  |

