1. the person playing scrabble is on the far right##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Flower    | dahlia        | balloon-flower | bellflower     |
| Pet       | bird | hamster          | frog |
| Game   | backgammon     | billiard          | scrabble       |

