.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-15::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, grey, yellow
There 3 different types of food: carrot, lettuce, mango
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car
1. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
2. the person eating carrot is the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who likes grey is the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |   3    |
| Color   | grey      | yellow | red |
| Food   | lettuce        | carrot         | mango |
| Transport           | airplane | car         | bike   |

