3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the spanish is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
6. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |
