.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-17::.
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, corn, pumpkin
City: rome, london, edinburgh
There are 3 different nationalities: italian, argentine, indian
1. the indian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating watermelon is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the italian##1
4. the person eating corn is the person traveling to london##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Food     | corn      | watermelon | pumpkin |
| City     | london | rome      | edinburgh           |
| Nationality   | indian | italian  | argentine    |

