3. the baccarat-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
5. the dancer is on the left of the mechanic##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |
| Job    | paramedic | dancer      | mechanic     |
| Cigar         | blend  | old-henry | baccarat        |
| Game   | canasta | whist    | billiard |

