.:: Puzzle 3x3-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, climbing, baseball
House: townhouse, craftsman, colonial
There 3 different types of food: pineapple, peach, raspberry
1. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is basketball and the craftsman house##2
2. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
4. the colonial house is the person eating peach##1
5. the colonial house is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
7. the townhouse house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
| Sport         | baseball      | climbing | basketball |
| House   | craftsman | townhouse      | colonial    |
| Food           | raspberry      | pineapple        | peach       |

 